{"id":"cde19f31-5930-4e7f-97a9-8481e0248514","name":"The dwellers Minecraft add on","description":"<p>Basically the Dwellers add-on from Minecraft. I was playing it and the unseen death was leaving signs and it lowkey sounded really hot…So yeah!</p><p>Here’s the link to learn more about the mod:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=2e5049f1-cf17-4fba-b60d-d1d92284e3bc\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=2e5049f1-cf17-4fba-b60d-d1d92284e3bc</a></p><p>I couldn’t find a picture of the Villager mimic, so just imagine a hot villager’s skin that being used by a skinwalker❤️ anyways here’s what each dweller looks like:</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6b5ca4df-4b70-407b-a30e-d88b8f8ad00e_777d18f5-8d6a-465b-8ec0-996498aa5236.webp?width=1000\">The All-seeing dweller</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6b5ca4df-4b70-407b-a30e-d88b8f8ad00e_352cbed8-57b7-4794-a7cb-7d9997151a8b.webp?width=1000\">The watchtower dweller</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6b5ca4df-4b70-407b-a30e-d88b8f8ad00e_dd4f2028-f097-4d1e-8831-886f72087acf.webp?width=1000\">The goatman dweller</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6b5ca4df-4b70-407b-a30e-d88b8f8ad00e_94a2d060-e1a5-40f3-b686-ed3880bc47f6.webp?width=1000\">The unseen death dweller</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6b5ca4df-4b70-407b-a30e-d88b8f8ad00e_25a5c975-274b-4693-8f9d-f31186cdc0f5.webp?width=1000\">The shadow dweller</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cu